# Enterprise Backend Architecture: HR E-Dossier System

This document outlines the complete, production-ready backend architecture for the HR E-Dossier system, designed to handle thousands of employees efficiently using Node.js, Express.js, Sequelize, and PostgreSQL.

## 1. Backend Project Folder Structure

```text
server/
├── src/
│   ├── config/
