## 9. Auto-Create Logic & Seed Data

**Auto-Creating Documents on Employee Registration:**
```javascript
// Inside employee.controller.js -> createEmployee
const newEmployee = await Employee.create(req.body);

// Fetch all categories
const allCategories = await DocumentCategory.findAll();

// Bulk create document stubs
const documentStubs = allCategories.map(cat => ({
    employee_id: newEmployee.id,
    category_id: cat.id,
    status: 'incomplete'
}));

await Document.bulkCreate(documentStubs);
```

